<h1>Video Cortex</h1>

<p>
    Turn YouTube videos into a compounding, per-project knowledge library. Create a project,
    paste in videos, and Video Cortex fetches the transcript, summarizes each one, and maintains
    a synthesized OKF-HTML report on disk.
</p>

<p class="muted">Foundation scaffold — projects, ingestion, and reports arrive in later phases.</p>
